# Richwell Portal — Complete API Endpoint Audit

> **Date:** 2026-03-11 | **Framework:** Django REST Framework + SimpleJWT  
> **Global Defaults:** `JWTAuthentication`, `IsAuthenticated`, Paginated (20/page), `DjangoFilterBackend` + `SearchFilter` + `OrderingFilter`

