## 1. Authentication (accounts)

| Path | Method | Auth | Permissions | Serializer | Request Body | Response | Errors |
|------|--------|------|-------------|------------|-------------|----------|--------|
| `api/accounts/auth/login/` | POST | No | `AllowAny` | [LoginSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/serializers.py#28-53) | `{username, password}` | `{access, refresh, user: {id, username, email, first_name, last_name, role, is_active, headed_programs}}` | 401 Invalid credentials |
| `api/accounts/auth/refresh/` | POST | No | `AllowAny` | SimpleJWT default | `{refresh}` | `{access, refresh}` | 401 Token invalid/expired |
| `api/accounts/auth/logout/` | POST | Yes | `IsAuthenticated` | None | — | `{detail: "Successfully logged out."}` | 401 |
| `api/accounts/auth/me/` | GET | Yes | `IsAuthenticated` | [UserSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/serializers.py#7-27) | — | `{id, username, email, first_name, last_name, role, is_active, headed_programs}` | 401 |
| `api/accounts/auth/change-password/` | PUT/PATCH | Yes | `IsAuthenticated` | [ChangePasswordSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/serializers.py#54-63) | `{old_password, new_password, confirm_password}` | `{detail: "Password updated successfully."}` | 400 Wrong password / Passwords don't match |

