## 2. Staff Management (accounts)

| Path | Method | Auth | Permissions | Serializer | Request Body | Response | Errors |
|------|--------|------|-------------|------------|-------------|----------|--------|
| `api/accounts/staff/` | GET | Yes | `IsAuthenticated, IsAdmin` | [UserSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/serializers.py#7-27) | — | Paginated list `{id, username, email, first_name, last_name, role, is_active, headed_programs}` | 401, 403 |
| `api/accounts/staff/` | POST | Yes | `IsAuthenticated, IsAdmin` | [StaffCreateSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/serializers.py#64-79) | `{username, email, first_name, last_name, role, is_active}` | `{id, username, email, first_name, last_name, role, is_active}` | 400 Validation |
| `api/accounts/staff/{id}/` | GET | Yes | `IsAuthenticated, IsAdmin` | [UserSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/serializers.py#7-27) | — | Single user object | 404 |
| `api/accounts/staff/{id}/` | PUT/PATCH | Yes | `IsAuthenticated, IsAdmin` | [StaffCreateSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/serializers.py#64-79) | `{username, email, first_name, last_name, role, is_active}` | Updated user | 400, 404 |
| `api/accounts/staff/{id}/` | DELETE | Yes | `IsAuthenticated, IsAdmin` | — | — | 204 | 404 |
| `api/accounts/staff/{id}/reset_password/` | POST | Yes | `IsAuthenticated, IsAdmin` | None | — | `{detail: "Password reset to {username}1234"}` | 404 |

> [!CAUTION]
> **[reset_password](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/views.py#89-96) returns the plaintext password in the response body.** This is a security risk.

