## 3. Academics

### Programs

| Path | Method | Auth | Permissions | Serializer | Request Body | Response | Errors |
|------|--------|------|-------------|------------|-------------|----------|--------|
| `api/academics/programs/` | GET | No* | [IsAdminOrReadOnly](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#91-101) | [ProgramSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/academics/serializers.py#37-51) | — | Paginated `{id, code, name, effective_year, has_summer, program_head, program_head_name, is_active, active_curriculum_id}` | — |
| `api/academics/programs/` | POST | Yes | [IsAdmin](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#9-14) | [ProgramSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/academics/serializers.py#37-51) | `{code, name, effective_year, has_summer, program_head}` | Created program | 400, 403 |
| `api/academics/programs/{id}/` | GET/PUT/PATCH/DELETE | Mixed | [IsAdminOrReadOnly](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#91-101) | [ProgramSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/academics/serializers.py#37-51) | — | Program object | 404 |

*Read methods allow unauthenticated access via [IsAdminOrReadOnly](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#91-101).

**Filters:** `is_active`, `has_summer` | **Search:** `code`, `name`

### Curriculum Versions

| Path | Method | Auth | Permissions | Serializer |
|------|--------|------|-------------|------------|
| `api/academics/curriculums/` | GET/POST | Mixed | [IsAdminOrReadOnly](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#91-101) | [CurriculumVersionSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/academics/serializers.py#29-36) |
| `api/academics/curriculums/{id}/` | GET/PUT/PATCH/DELETE | Mixed | [IsAdminOrReadOnly](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#91-101) | [CurriculumVersionSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/academics/serializers.py#29-36) |
| `api/academics/curriculums/{id}/set_active/` | POST | Yes | [IsAdmin](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#9-14) | — |

**Response fields:** `{id, program, program_code, version_name, is_active, subject_count, created_at}`  
**Filters:** [program](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/serializers.py#16-21), `is_active`

### Subjects

| Path | Method | Auth | Permissions | Serializer |
|------|--------|------|-------------|------------|
| `api/academics/subjects/` | GET/POST | Mixed | [IsAdminOrReadOnly](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#91-101) | [SubjectSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/academics/serializers.py#16-28) |
| `api/academics/subjects/{id}/` | GET/PUT/PATCH/DELETE | Mixed | [IsAdminOrReadOnly](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#91-101) | [SubjectSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/academics/serializers.py#16-28) |
