**Response fields:** `{id, curriculum, curriculum_name, program_code, code, description, year_level, semester, lec_units, lab_units, total_units, hrs_per_week, is_major, is_practicum, prerequisites[]}`  
**Filters:** [curriculum](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/academics/serializers.py#48-51), `curriculum__program`, `year_level`, `semester`, `is_major` | **Search:** `code`, `description`  
