## 5. Students

| Path | Method | Auth | Permissions | Serializer | Request Body | Response | Errors |
|------|--------|------|-------------|------------|-------------|----------|--------|
| `api/students/` | GET | Yes | `IsAuthenticated` | [StudentSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/students/serializers.py#10-43) | — | Paginated students list | 401 |
| `api/students/{id}/` | GET/PUT/PATCH/ DELETE | Yes | `IsAuthenticated` | [StudentSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/students/serializers.py#10-43) | — | Student object | 401, 404 |
| `api/students/apply/` | POST | No | `AllowAny` | [StudentApplicationSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/students/serializers.py#44-61) | `{first_name, last_name, email, middle_name, date_of_birth, gender, address_municipality, address_barangay, address_full, contact_number, guardian_name, guardian_contact, program, curriculum, student_type, previous_school}` | Created student | 400 Duplicate email |
| `api/students/{id}/approve/` | POST | Yes | [IsAdmission](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#30-35) | None (manual) | `{monthly_commitment}` | `{student, credentials: {idn, password}}` | 400, 500 |
| `api/students/{id}/unlock_advising/` | POST | Yes | `IsRegistrar \| IsAdmin` | — | — | `{status: "Advising process unlocked"}` | 404 |
| `api/students/{id}/toggle_regularity/` | POST | Yes | `IsRegistrar \| IsAdmin` | — | `{is_regular}` | `{status, is_regular}` | 400 |
| `api/students/{id}/returning_student/` | POST | Yes | `IsAuthenticated` | — | `{monthly_commitment}` | `{message, enrollment}` | 400, 403 |
| `api/students/manual_add/` | POST | Yes | `IsRegistrar \| IsAdmin` | — | `{idn, email, first_name, last_name, date_of_birth, gender, program, curriculum, student_type, year_level, monthly_commitment}` | `{message, student, is_regular}` | 400 |

> [!CAUTION]
> **[approve](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/students/views.py#81-160) endpoint returns plaintext password** `{credentials: {idn, password}}` in the response.

**Filters:** [status](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/finance/views.py#68-82), `student_type`, [program](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/accounts/serializers.py#16-21) | **Search:** `user__first_name`, `user__last_name`, `user__email`, `idn`

