| `api/faculty/professors/{id}/subjects/` | GET | Yes | [IsStaff](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#79-89) | [ProfessorSubjectSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/faculty/serializers.py#8-23) | 404 |
| `api/faculty/professors/{id}/subjects/` | POST | Yes | [IsStaff](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#79-89) | None (manual) | 404 |
| `api/faculty/professors/{id}/assign_subjects/` | POST | Yes | [IsStaff](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/core/permissions.py#79-89) | None (manual) | 404 |
