## 9. Finance (Payments)

| Path | Method | Auth | Permissions | Serializer | Errors |
|------|--------|------|-------------|------------|--------|
| `api/finance/payments/` | GET | Yes | Global default | [PaymentSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/finance/serializers.py#4-19) | 401 |
| `api/finance/payments/` | POST | Yes | Global default | [PaymentSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/finance/serializers.py#4-19) | 400 |
| `api/finance/payments/{id}/` | GET | Yes | Global default | [PaymentSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/finance/serializers.py#4-19) | 404 |
| `api/finance/payments/{id}/` | PUT/PATCH | Yes | — | — | **405 Always** |
| `api/finance/payments/{id}/` | DELETE | Yes | — | — | **405 Always** |
| `api/finance/payments/adjust/` | POST | Yes | Global default | [PaymentSerializer](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/finance/serializers.py#4-19) | 400 |

**Request body (create/adjust):** `{student, term, month, amount, is_promissory, remarks}`  
**Response fields:** `{id, student, student_idn, student_name, term, month, amount, entry_type, entry_type_display, is_promissory, remarks, processed_by, processed_by_name, created_at}`

> [!WARNING]
> **No explicit permission_classes set** on [PaymentViewSet](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/richwell-potal/backend/apps/finance/views.py#9-64). Falls back to global `IsAuthenticated` only. No role-based restriction (e.g., Cashier-only).

